    "",
    "**c)** Componentwise: (k+m)a₁ = k a₁ + m a₁ ✓",
    "",
    "**d)** 1×v + 1×v = 2v ✓",
    "",
    "### Exercise 7: Associativity of Scalar Multiplication",
    "",
    "**a)** Left: $2(3\\vec{a}) = 2\\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ 6 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} 6 \\\\ 12 \\end{pmatrix}$",
    "Right: $(2×3)\\vec{a} = 6\\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 2 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} 6 \\\\ 12 \\end{pmatrix}$ ✓",
