    "",
    "**d)** Scalars multiply in any order.",
    "",
    "### Exercise 8: Scalar Multiplication by 1 and 0",
    "",
    "**a)** $1 \\times \\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ 4 \\\\ 5 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ 4 \\\\ 5 \\end{pmatrix}$ ✓",
